Dialogue: None today, I'm afraid...
Could use more dzo meat!
I'll pass it along!

Catch of the day!
Fresh from the Ruby Sea!
Bah, I can't decide...
Hands where I can see...
Show us what you've got!
I'm not afraid... But it is awfully high, isn't it?
Stop making excuses and go!
It's a long way down...
\\<pant> It's a miracle I survived...
So this is where it starts getting tricky?

Pirates lose to ninjas?
Over my dead body!
I can't do it... I can't do it!
It all hangs on this final stage...

How could I shame myself so
in front of my beloved?
If only I were a ninja!
I knew you'd reach the top!

I wasn't watching.
Could you do that again for me?

Of all the ones to complete the course,
you're my favorite!

Come one, come all!
The Moonfire Faire is here!

Adventurers! Test your
skills on the Eorzean
Nimble Warrior course!
Come on, let's go for a swim!
Shall we go and watch?

It's certainly impressive,
but it's a bit of an eyesore...
I wonder what Master Gegeruju is like?
There's always time for squats!

In the way?
No, not at all!

Finish the course?
We're too busy looking good!
Mustn't...let go...
Argh! Stop shaking it!
And this is the easy part!?
Am I truly ready?
I know you're not supposed to fall off, but it is quite fun!

I'm not drowning,
I'm just resting.

I mustn't give in to
my fear next time...
I must focus.

\\<splutter> Gods!
Am I dead!?
Is that all you've got!?
That's the way! Just a little farther!
You're almost there!
Let me know when someone promising shows up.
I had a feeling that Lalafell chap would struggle...
I could watch this all day!

And I need a long, hot bath!
We've all got to wait our turn!
This is no small order...
But are they absolutely, perfectly parallel...?
Will these do?
Give me a moment!

Shipment ought to be
arriving soon, I think...

About time! This saw's got
no teeth left to speak of...
Hey, about those tools─

Not today, I'm afraid.
Delivery's been delayed.
Again...
...Heard that?

Aye. Should've known.
We'll make do as always...
The lighter the better...
Aren't we spoiled for choice...
Pine it is!

...And then the handle split
right down the middle!

Surely there's got to be
something I can do...
...Or not. Back to my bunk.
Really can't be bothered...
A little more and it'll be finished! You'll see!
Impressive craftsmanship...

Just watching everyone work
makes me feel...I don't know...
...Like we've turned a corner?

Excellent work! This should be
more than enough!
We'll need to add ash soon...

Arms holding up? Even
though it's been a while?
I could do this all day!
Looking good...
Hurrrgh!
By the kami, I'm spent!
No, this isn't the place.
...Just tell me where to take it.

What did the Shazenkai
fellow say again?
I wonder where he went...

Really, it's far too much for
the elders to handle...

...Actually, I, uh, I don't
really like heights...
Anyone here caught cheating answers to me, understand?
Next time. Next time I'll hit the cactpot.

A present? But it's not
even my nameday!

Hells take your cards!
I say we race chocobos!
We should play Triple Triad!

Don't stray too far,
got that? I promised to
keep an eye on you.
I will have that bunny suit!
'Tis your mind playing tricks on you. Nothing more.
I swear I've seen him somewhere before...

You ladies head up first.
I'll take the rear...

You'll take my pickaxe to the
eye should you try anything.
Don't be such a ssspoilsport.

Such magnificent muscles.
Heh heh heh...

When the children are happy,
Zhloe's happy too!
I love festivals, don't you, T'kebbe?

This is so much fun!
Thank you, Miss Zhloe!
Some of the wood is missing...
How fare you this <If(LessThan(PlayerParameter(11),12))><If(LessThan(PlayerParameter(11),4))>evening<Else/>day</If><Else/><If(LessThan(PlayerParameter(11),17))>day<Else/>evening</If></If>?
Well enough, well enough.
Working hard, or hardly working?
Having the time of my life!
Hah! Well, try not to overdo it.
Like...like this?
Shall I set it down by the reclamation box?
Aye, if it's no trouble!
Not at all.
More for the pile!
Ah, where to put it...
Don't rush on my account.
Where could he be...?
Medicine... I need more...

Sorry, friend, but I'm
short this one herb...
If I had it, I could sort you out.
...Tell me where it grows.
Hnnngh...
Graaaghhh...
Grrrrrr...
\\<smack> \\<slurp>

What good's wine when it
freezes in the bloody bottle?
（★未使用／削除予定★）
（★未使用／削除予定★）
Ahh, feel that heat!

Gerolt's definitely got a knack
for more than weapons.
Think it's worth digging out?

Depends on who's got to
do the digging.

Wonder if it'll cook faster
if we keep staring.

Eh, not like I've got
anywhere else to be...

A place for everything and
everything in its place...

Even a shallow well
shouldn't freeze like this!
Thisss place is a maze!
Kageyama must not escape us.
If I have calculated the rice-per-fulm ratio correctly...
This is awfully thirsty work!
I have come to harvest your souls! Errr...I mean rice.
Picking up all these stones is not my idea of fun.
So, how does it look?
Full of weeds and stones, I'm afraid.
“Many hands make light work,” they say.
I spy some more weeds that want pulling up.
It may not be lifelike, but it keeps the crows away!
Oh...I knew I should've labeled these boxes.
Hold still so I can get this mud out of your fur!

In the morning, laughing happy fish heads.♪
In the evening, floating in the soup!♪
And now for my secret ingredient... Once I find it, anyway.
I'm telling you! We should be making sake!
The nail that sticks out gets hammered down.
I suppose I will have to climb down at some point.
What should we use for the roof?
Zelkova should do the trick.
Leave it to me!
Ummm... Which ones are zelkova?
Carry the timber up the ladder? Easier said than done!
Just like carrying a wife over the threshold. But with timber.
What do you have in mind?
Should be ready in a few bells...
What's this? When in Doma, Do as the Domans Do: A Guide for Ijin...
“The Eorzean diet largely consists of popotoes rather than rice.”
I was just resting my eyes!
All this reading is making me sleepy!
Spinny spin spin!
Tell me more about Eorzea!
I wonder who carried all these big crates?
Seems straight enough to me.
I'll be a lot happier once we get that roof up!
Can't have any of these logs rolling off and squashing someone!
And she told me to mind my own business!
Perhaps I will have more luck with this one?

I'm not pushing myself up,
I'm pushing the earth down!

I hear squats cure baldness!
If not, I could always buy a wig...
Not a bad selection.
Put your back into it, lad!
These are the resources we need from the Shazenkai.
These should hold up...
Gah! No more nails! I'll just keep tapping these ones, then.
Would somebody open the door, please?
I could swear I heard a voice...
What should we do with all these leftover explosives?
Why don't I take over?
Take this, Garlean...rubble!
By the kami, it's hot out here!
Say, friend, you are looking rather “board.” Hur hur!

I wandered lonely as a pond...
No, that doesn't sound right...

Never, never again!
This I do solemnly swear...
No one is allowed past this point.
But I must have those herbs!

I'm looking for a Lupin boy.
Have you seen him?
Can't say I have.
We cannot see anything from here!
As soon as this is finished, we go in search of Hien!
Wretched cat...I was only trying to help! Now I'm the one who needs saving!
Meow!
I am a bunshin, yes, yes.

Shapeshifter, eh? Show me
what you've got!

Heh, all right!
I'll show you “you”!

How 'bout it?
We could be twins!
A rat? A rat!? I am an otter, good sir!
We once had cuisine...
Possibilities abound...
A bold move...
See a fire, raise the alarum!

At last, the scales have
fallen from my eyes...

Eyes bigger than
my stomach...
How about...this!?

Eh. Same as the last
two dozen times...
I could just drift off...

You really shouldn't,
you know...

There, there,
that's a good girl...
Kweh, kweh!
I ain't no bloody miner...

Yes, well, we've all got
to help however we can.

We ain't gotta dream
no more...

Help wanted! High wages!
Meals provided!
Things are starting to look up.
Right, then. Let's be about it!

If the terms are to my liking.
I've got options, you know.

Folks can say what they like.
I'd still hold your purse close.

Past time we had
proper materials.
Bloody oath.

Aye, I got a job. Still living
in a bloody tent for all
the good it's done me.

It's better than before,
but that ain't saying much...
Today, we work...
Tomorrow, we eat the rich!

Pulled me groin
with all that honest work─

Whatever you're about
to ask, don't.

So one of those fat merchants
offered to make me his slave...

Me too. Let's both say yes
and kill him while he sleeps.

It's not the same
without them.

Perhaps we too should
return to Ala Mhigo...
Thus begins my empire...

You'll be buying it
for a good deal more!

What ever do you have
in that pot? It smells
absolutely heavenly!

Some of Stonesthrow's
extra-special stew, sir!

You an old customer?
Sorry, but I don't do that
kind of work anymore.

What shall I treat
the boy to today...?
Fair enough, fair enough...
The rabble's in high spirits...
You have been in that pot long enough, yes, yes?
Why must you torment me, you furry fiend!?
My, what big ears you have!
All the better to hear you with.
What do you mean by that?
Hien would never expect us to chase after him in a boat!
Is this the only way? I'm feeling a little queasy...
You're welcome to swim alongside, if you prefer!
Considering how long we spent on that boat, we must be in Eorzea by now.
Brothers, down here! Help me!
Do you think we'll see those Budugan men again?
Well, last I heard, they're heading west from Kugane.
They still haven't given up on Lord Hien, then...
You have to admire their determination, if nothing else.

My Ala Mhigan contacts
are up to the challenge.

This selection is impressive,
but I'm looking for something
especially rare...

What were you expecting?
A sabotender?
Fungahhhhhh!
That's the way!

Steady your hand
and aim true.
I have a feeling your talents lie elsewhere...
Perhaps I should craft us an egg instead?
Matron's teats! How did I let them talk me into this?
A new chapter in the legend of M'zhet Tia begins today!
A self-proclaimed future nunh he may be, but a puzzle-solving genius he is not.
Oh! You two have made a new friend!
He's so warm and fluffy! Can I keep him?
Watch your fingers, Khloe! He looks sort of...bitey to me.
It seems I must petition the elementals for aid.
Spiky man! Scary man!
Fancy seeing you here...
By the kami, what now...

For our next bit, all three
of us will double “you”!

Don't do it! Don't you dare
pull a Genbu!

Perish the thought!
Now watch!

How 'bout it?
We could be quadruplets!

Oh, well done you!
I'm sure no one saw
that one coming! Bah!
W-Would you like to try the ceremony with me?
I'd love to!

Hah!
One more time, then.
Let's go again, Granddad!
The bulletin... Have to check the bulletin...
Heh heh, clowns are funny.
Did you check the bulletin?
I...uh... No, miss...
\\<sigh> Go. Check. The bulletin.
Over there, eh?
Huh? Was sure this is the spot...
Has to be here, then!
...No? Godsdammit!
Where's this supposed to go?
What now, do you think?
Haven't you stared long enough?
No, it's not nearly seared into my brain!
Well, if the vegetables go over there...
I pray this will be enough.

We have no reason to believe
the barrier will not hold.

Yet if they should bring
all to bear against us...

We should send out a
reconnaissance team.
I will do whatever it takes to save my patients. Whatever it takes!

There's nothin' more beautiful
than a sunset on the Rhotano.
I pray I live to see it...

I fear we lack the numbers
to hold out...

Then we must call for
reinforcements.
We must protect the border at all costs.
Till our dyin' breaths.
Argh...
I can't feel my legs...

Only once before have
I bowed my head low...
My body is ready for a hot meal.
As soon as our watch is over.
Gods, what I wouldn't give for a bath...
●仮設定
That doesn't look half bad...
Sure, I'll give it a try.
I'd buy that for a gil...
Down the hatch!
The path to riches is a perilous one, yes, yes...

Seven hells!
Get a bloody room, will ye!?
The next match is mine!

Mewling cub!
You'll never defeat me!
I'll show ye how to swing a damn hammer!
The abyss take me...
Wh-Which tile should I discard...?
Well, this is a disaster!
And one is meant to scale this edifice...?
Ulalaaa!
I love you!
Mashaaa!
Yes!
U-lah-lah!
Hah! Hah!
Narumiii!
She looked at me!
W-We're safe...?
The sky...
What's happening...?
Lord...Vauthry...
Long may...you reign...
Ohhh...
Hallowed be his name...
Blessed is the meol...
Is this supposed to be part of the show?
Something's happening...
Did you summon those things!?
What in the gods' name is that!?
That way! The crown's that way!
Keep running! You're almost there!
Phew, we did it...
Time to collect our prize.
I daresay they've had their fill of sport.
Is... Is it over?
Their mastery over glamours is truly astounding.

It was no less than what
I expected, but─well done.
Alisaie...
Rest well...

A Lightwarden, gone.
I can scarce believe it.

Good. Keep that
memory with you.
That Lightwarden... That was terrifying.
And thus doth the night return.
So the Warden of the wood falls.
We've taken back the darkness!
At last.
It seems that Ryne was correct.
Thank goodness we succeeded.

That was a passing
strange form for an eater.
Are you at all injured?
Vauthry awaits.
It's the moment of truth.

No eaters remain to
stand in our way.

I feel it above─
a powerful light.
All has gone to plan thus far. ...To the extent there is a plan.

An eater that only makes
the others fiercer. Lovely.
We shall not falter!
Not for despair, nor fate itself.

Be on your guard.
This is wholly his realm.
Where is Emet-Selch?

This is it─the
first and final end.
The unwinding of life itself...
One cannot help but pity Vauthry...
Finally, all the Lightwardens are gone...
Come out, come out, wherever you are!
What should we do when we find them?
We send them flying! Tee hee!
Aaany moment now...
D-Don't let them eat me!
What in the world...?
What's wrong with everyone?
Where...where am I?
Ungh... My head...
Long live...Lord Vauthry?
It was awful... \\<sob>
Are you all right?
Zzzzzz...
\\<snore> \\<snore>
\\<slurp> \\<snort>
Wake up, damn you!
What's happening!?
It's the dust! Don't breathe in the dust!
Keep an eye on them buggers!
We're gonna need more meat...
Who's a pretty girl, then?
I think...\\<hic>...I've had enough...
Whisk, whisk until it's mixed!♪

Grab a seat!
...And a mug!
You do too much...
Ugh, I need a drink...
Aye, that hits the spot!
Lali-hooo!
La... La...li...ho!
Hup! Ha!
No swivin' Goggs about, then?
B-Blast! It's higher than I thought...
No rips that I can see...
Heading in for a pint?
We've got to protect our food stores!
Is there aught else you need?
I'm fine for now, thanks.
Just a few more rows!
Hey! We're meant to do our chores first!
Wait!
I'm gonna get you!
Yay! I got you!
Nuh-uh! I let you catch me!
That's enough! You're both winners.
Let's play catch-the-kitten!
All right, you go first!
This way, slowpoke!
Almost time to eat!
W-We'll get you some medicine...
It's gotta be cooked by now...
Did you hear what happened to that girl!?
That ought to keep the wind out.

Please...
Whatever you can spare...
Maybe I should join him...
But the letter from the Crystarium said...
I hope this crop turns out better than the last...
Don't you wag your finger at me!
I once knew twins who had hair just like yours!
We'd best scout the area first.
You can cross that bridge when you come to it.
The forest calls to me...
I am not lying! I saw it!
Well, if the others don't get here soon, we'll have to eat their share!
Give me a moment, would you? I'm sure it's crooked!
That is what Uimet said, anyway.
It is probably true, in that case.
Is everything ready?
Master Lanille has taken care of it.
Then I shall return to my post.
I'd better count them again, just to be sure.
Yes, yes! Adorable!
There must be at least one shiny here!
Not a bad price, all things considered.
I'll get us a good deal, don't you worry!
Now, you stay right there!
Hmm? Where did it go?
I take my eyes off of it for one moment...
Come back here!
Not again!
Not good, not good...
There it is!
You must not wander off like that, understood?
That's a fair point...
I have a feeling I've forgotten something.
Come now, you mustn't fret.

It never ceases to amaze.
Every time I see it...
What am I supposed to do now!?
A tasty morsel of information, yes?
Leave no stone unturned...
To see a sin eater from so close... I will never forget it.
And we'll split the profits!
Yes, it's all here, as agreed.
So, ready to get back to work?
Not yet. Still coughing up grey phlegm.
Erm... You might wanna get that looked at...
The Fuath are nothing but trouble!
As my master always used to say...
Yes, better than boiling them, methinks.
A fair trade, it would seem.
A bit on the small side, perhaps...
Slowly but surely do the mushrooms grow.
The blue one... Or the other blue one... Hmm...
I am sure my eyesight is getting worse.
Oh! This is a heavy one!
Gather round, little ones.
And we'll call it “Delta Attack!”
Let's try shapechanging!
That sounds like fun!
Watch this!
Ooh! I can't wait to see this!
Piff, paff, poff!
Eek!
Oink!
Hee hee! How terribly amusing!
Haha! A porxie!
Oink! Oink!
Now I just need to work out how to reverse it...
Wait for me!
Come back!
Ummm...
It's a beaver!
Snook!
You'll never catch me!
Snook! Chit!
